    "Furthermore, the authors in [3] utilize human feedback to enhance the configurations generated by the LLM, hindering their ability to ensure intent assurance autonomously.",
    "We propose to go beyond this basic setup of [3].",
    "Specifically, we propose to employ LMMs for various phases in intent management spanned across the OSI layers:• Problem formulation phase: In intent-based wireless networks, the operator expresses business intents in simple natural language.",
    "The network autonomously translates these intents into an optimization problem, considering multiple objectives and physical constraints.",
    "An LMM can facilitate dynamic problem formulation without human intervention."
  ],
